<\/p>","link_url":"shopify:\/\/collections\/vertus","button_label":"Tout voir","color_scheme":"none","button_style":"link"}},"custom_collection_list_DyzFfG":{"type":"custom-collection-list","blocks":{"collection_9JgzHc":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"famille"}},"collection_RHBK8P":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"nature"}},"collection_BbhEmM":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"lart"}},"collection_hTCX3K":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"la-religion"}},"collection_Gp6wYH":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"psychologie-et-affectivite","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Psychologie.png"}},"collection_DwmxfV":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"animaux"}},"collection_bYUhqq":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"scoutisme"}},"collection_BBFqwM":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"voyage"}}},"block_order":["collection_9JgzHc","collection_RHBK8P","collection_BbhEmM","collection_hTCX3K","collection_Gp6wYH","collection_DwmxfV","collection_bYUhqq","collection_BBFqwM"],"custom_css":[".card__collection .media {background-color: #97e8c733;}",".card-link {display: none;}"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_align":"text-start","view_more_label":"","view_more_link":"","layout":"carousel","card_size_mobile":"small","card_size":"small","show_promo_info":true,"image_ratio":"natural","promo_title":"Centres d'intérêts","content":"<p>Parcourez les grands centres d'intérêts susceptibles d'enthousiasmer vos enfants et éveiller leur curiosité : Artistes en herbe, Découverte de la nature, Mes émotions, Le corps humain, Les couleurs, ou encore Le coin des parents pour vous aider à les accompagner.<\/p>","link_url":"shopify:\/\/collections\/centres-d-interets","button_label":"Tout voir","color_scheme":"none","button_style":"link"}},"custom_collection_list_mExcG9":{"type":"custom-collection-list","blocks":{"collection_mQYzyh":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"poesies"}},"collection_Pi3JTg":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"contes"}},"collection_9FWbjL":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"grands-auteurs"}},"collection_pVgexP":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"aventures"}},"collection_QbrmqL":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"antiquite-et-mythologie"}},"collection_N39keQ":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"fantastique"}},"collection_gjMe4b":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"histoires-vraies-biographies"}},"collection_dKG7Dz":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"romans-policiers"}},"collection_bjfWth":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"histoire"}},"collection_zEt7HJ":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"abecedaires-et-imagiers"}}},"block_order":["collection_mQYzyh","collection_Pi3JTg","collection_9FWbjL","collection_pVgexP","collection_QbrmqL","collection_N39keQ","collection_gjMe4b","collection_dKG7Dz","collection_bjfWth","collection_zEt7HJ"],"custom_css":[".card__collection .media {background-color: #f6cc6c33;}",".card-link {display: none;}"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_align":"text-start","view_more_label":"","view_more_link":"","layout":"carousel","card_size_mobile":"small","card_size":"small","show_promo_info":true,"image_ratio":"natural","promo_title":"Genres littéraires","content":"<p>Cherchez une lecture pour vos enfants parmi les Grands auteurs, les Poésies, les Contes, Légendes et Mythologies, les Aventures, les Bandes dessinées et Manga et bien d'autres genres littéraires.<\/p>","link_url":"shopify:\/\/collections\/genres-litteraires","button_label":"Tout voir","color_scheme":"none","button_style":"link"}},"boutons_collection_B4JieG":{"type":"boutons-collection","blocks":{"button_xhHrFn":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"Tout-petits","button_link":"tout-petits"}},"button_nc7TeG":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"2 à 4 ans","button_link":"avant-4-ans"}},"button_tndUJx":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"4 à 6 ans","button_link":"de-4-a-6-ans"}},"button_zyAjyJ":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"6 à 8 ans","button_link":"de-6-a-8-ans"}},"button_7BHgKp":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"8 à 10 ans","button_link":"de-8-a-10-ans"}},"button_Jgwb3c":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"10 à 12 ans","button_link":"de-10-a-12-ans"}},"button_tMBVYb":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"12 à 14 ans","button_link":"de-12-a-14-ans"}},"button_pMkHpV":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"Après 14 ans","button_link":"apres-14-ans"}}},"block_order":["button_xhHrFn","button_nc7TeG","button_tndUJx","button_zyAjyJ","button_7BHgKp","button_Jgwb3c","button_tMBVYb","button_pMkHpV"],"settings":{"heading":"Trouvez le livre idéal selon l'âge de votre enfant","description":"Chaque enfant évolue à son propre rythme, et choisir un livre adapté à son âge est essentiel pour stimuler son imagination, enrichir son vocabulaire et nourrir son amour de la lecture. C’est pourquoi nous avons classé nos collections en différentes tranches d’âge, pour vous aider à trouver les ouvrages les plus adaptés aux besoins et aux envies de votre enfant, qu'il soit en pleine découverte des images, en apprentissage de la lecture ou déjà passionné par les romans.","background_color":"#f5faf9","button_color":"#8fcdbf","margin_top":0,"margin_bottom":0}},"custom_text_block_VgrjPd":{"type":"custom-text-block","disabled":true,"custom_css":["div {max-width: 1220px;}","@media (min-width: 1040px) {div {margin-bottom: -70px; }}"],"name":"Bloc texte avancé","settings":{"title":"Notre mission","title_anchor_id":"","mobile_center":true,"heading_tag":"h2","heading_style_class":"h3","text":"","text_align":"left","p_align":"left","title_margin_top":"50","title_margin_bottom":"-10","p_margin_top":"","p_margin_bottom":""}},"media_with_text_8pht4Q":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"text_HNPM4j":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Verty est née d'une conviction simple : Dans un monde où les écrans captent de plus en plus l’attention dès le plus jeune âge, nous croyons plus que jamais en la puissance irremplaçable du livre. Chaque histoire peut devenir une racine, chaque page une graine d’espérance et d’émerveillement, qui nourrit l’imaginaire et fait grandir en profondeur. Notre ambition est de simplifier la vie des parents et embellir celle des enfants à travers une marketplace qui ne rassemble que des livres soigneusement sélectionnés, pour que chaque enfant puisse s'élever page après page.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}},"button_w9HXVw":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"En savoir plus","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/a-propos","button_style":"btn btn--primary"}}},"block_order":["text_HNPM4j","button_w9HXVw"],"disabled":true,"custom_css":["picture {padding-left: 0;}",".media-with-text__text {padding-top: 65px;}"],"name":"Media with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/citation_michel_desmurget_hdf.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none","only_content_color_scheme":false}},"testimonials_k7EmXd":{"type":"testimonials","disabled":true,"custom_css":[".testimonials .testimonials__slide--no-padding {background-color: #8fcdbf; color: black; padding: 20px;}"],"name":"Testimonial Michel Desmurget","settings":{"heading":"","show_quotes":true,"testimonial_size":"h6","text_position":"justify-center","text_align":"text-center justify-center","nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":false,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"default","full_width":true}},"custom_media_with_text_kwqXxT":{"type":"custom-media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_Hh437C":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Une sélection à travers notre matrice vertueuse","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"text_mkdcdk":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Les livres alimentent les connaissances et l’imagination de nos enfants, ils développent leur empathie et nourrissent leur humanité. Parce que l'enfant, s'identifiant au héros, découvre le monde tel qu'il lui est décrit au fil des pages, il est nécessaire de veiller à lui proposer un contenu susceptible de l'élever et de l'éveiller à ce qui est beau et bon. Notre matrice vertueuse est inspirée du “carré magique” d’Une bibliothèque idéale. Pour être sélectionné, un contenu doit répondre à au moins 3 des 4 critères.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}},"button_QnwpYV":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"En savoir plus","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/a-propos","button_style":"btn btn--primary"}}},"block_order":["heading_Hh437C","text_mkdcdk","button_QnwpYV"],"disabled":true,"custom_css":[".section--padded,.section--padded-default {padding: 0px; padding-top: 40px;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Matrice_recto.png","second_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Matrice_verso.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"right","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none","only_content_color_scheme":false}},"testimonials_DUWRp9":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_bFgCb6":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>Des livres beaux, simples et vrais, qui nourrissent l'esprit et cultivent l'imaginaire des enfants<\/p>","author":"","author_info":"Author information","show_star_rating":false,"star_rating":5}}},"block_order":["testimonial_bFgCb6"],"custom_css":[".testimonials .testimonials__slide--no-padding {background-color: #8fcdbf; color: black; padding: 20px;}"],"name":"Testimonial Des livres beaux, simples...","settings":{"heading":"","show_quotes":true,"testimonial_size":"h6","text_position":"justify-center","text_align":"text-center justify-center","nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":false,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"default","full_width":true}},"e7a74f68-db1b-427c-aa28-4acb82159883":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"6caf8419-36f4-4f87-9ede-b3570cf7ddeb":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Des avis élaborés par notre comité de lecture","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"6db5bb2b-9cbf-4277-876d-88dce1e05b51":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Le comité de lecture a pour mission de sélectionner des livres écrits dans une belle langue. Il s'attache à la qualité esthétique, propre à éveiller l'enfant à l'art. Enfin, il veille à ce que le livre porte un regard positif sur le monde et soit cohérent avec les valeurs morales et les repères traditionnels qui fondent nos sociétés judéo-chrétiennes. <\/p>","enlarge_text":false}},"button_aeBcLB":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"En savoir plus","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/a-propos","button_style":"btn btn--primary"}}},"block_order":["6caf8419-36f4-4f87-9ede-b3570cf7ddeb","6db5bb2b-9cbf-4277-876d-88dce1e05b51","button_aeBcLB"],"custom_css":[".section--padded,.section--padded-default {padding: 0px;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/mother-with-little-daughter-sitting-plaid-read-book.jpg","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none","only_content_color_scheme":false}},"testimonials_qrxytn":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_kGqxyD":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>Des grands-parents et parents, institutrice, psychologue et orthophoniste<\/p>","author":"","author_info":"Author information","show_star_rating":false,"star_rating":5}}},"block_order":["testimonial_kGqxyD"],"custom_css":[".testimonials .testimonials__slide--no-padding {background-color: #8fcdbf; color: black; padding: 20px;}"],"name":"Testimonial Des grands-parents...","settings":{"heading":"","show_quotes":true,"testimonial_size":"h6","